(
  'doximity',
  'Doximity',
  'Professional network and AI tools for US physicians',
  E'Doximity is the professional network for US physicians, used by over 80% of US doctors. Beyond the networking and directory function, Doximity has built a suite of AI-powered clinical productivity tools accessible to its verified physician user base. The Doximity AI tool generates clinical letters, referral letters, prior authorisation letters, and patient communication drafts from brief prompts  -  the physician describes what needs to be communicated and Doximity drafts the full text.\n\nThe clinical communication tools address a specific administrative burden: physicians spending time writing and rewriting standard letters that follow predictable structures. Doximity''s AI generates these drafts instantly and lets physicians edit rather than write from scratch. The platform also provides secure HIPAA-compliant messaging between physicians for care coordination and a HIPAA-compliant video calling function.\n\nDoximity''s differentiation is access: verified US physicians get access to the AI tools through the existing Doximity platform they already use, without a separate procurement or integration step. For the 80%+ of US physicians already on Doximity, the AI features are an immediate productivity upgrade available through their existing login. The core platform is free for physicians; premium features including the advanced AI tools are available through the subscription tier.',
