(
  'anterior',
  'Anterior',
  'AI clinical intelligence for healthcare prior authorisation',
  E'Anterior is an AI platform that automates prior authorisation workflows for health systems and payers. Prior authorisation  -  the process by which insurers review and approve or deny medical procedures before they occur  -  is one of the most administratively burdensome processes in US healthcare, consuming significant time for both provider teams submitting requests and payer teams reviewing them.\n\nAnterior''s AI reviews the clinical evidence in a patient''s record, matches it against payer policy criteria, and generates a pre-populated prior authorisation submission including the relevant clinical justification drawn from the patient''s documented history. For reviewers on the payer side, Anterior surfaces the relevant clinical context alongside incoming requests to accelerate review. The platform integrates with EHR and payer systems to automate data flow between submission and review.\n\nAnterior is founded by physicians and focuses specifically on the prior auth workflow rather than broader clinical documentation. For health systems where prior auth administrative burden is a significant operational problem  -  often requiring dedicated staff teams and causing treatment delays  -  Anterior targets the specific inefficiency with purpose-built AI rather than a general-purpose documentation tool adapted to the use case.',
  'https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=anterior.com&sz=64',
  'https://anterior.com',
  'https://anterior.com',
  ARRAY['healthcare'],
  'paid',
  false,
  0.00,
  4.5,
  89,
  false, false, false,
  ARRAY['Purpose-built for prior authorisation  -  not a repurposed general tool', 'Automates clinical evidence extraction for PA submissions', 'Works for both health system submitters and payer reviewers', 'Reduces prior auth delays and associated treatment wait times', 'Integrates with EHR systems for automated data extraction'],
  ARRAY['US healthcare-specific workflow  -  limited international applicability', 'Enterprise procurement required  -  no self-serve access', 'ROI dependent on prior auth volume  -  less valuable for low-volume practices'],
